cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM

The paper deals with visual recognition and learning, which is primarily a computer vision (cs.CV) problem. The use of meta-learning techniques and neural networks for optimization suggests that the paper may also belong to the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper involves the use of image deformation techniques, which may also fall under the multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category. Finally, the use of fusion techniques and optimization methods may also suggest the paper belongs to the neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE) sub-category.
